    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-08-02</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-02-08T17:15:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Super Pollutants Act of 2019 </b></p> <p>This bill generally provides for the reduction of emissions of black carbon, methane, and certain hydrofluorocarbons (also referred to as short-lived climate pollutants) through policy initiatives of specified federal agencies. The bill also requires the President to establish the Interagency Task Force on Short-Lived Climate Pollutant Mitigation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Super Pollutants Act of 2019</title>
